				<h2>Manage Personal Information</h2>

				<p>Please go to the 'Personal' Page. You can do:</p>

				<ul style="margin-left: 20px;">
					<li>1.View Personal Information</li>
					<li>2.Change Password</li>
					<li>3.View borrowed list and favorite list (Only for General
