					<li>4.View To-Do-List (Only for staffs)</li>
				</ul>

				<br />

				<h2>Search Shortest Path</h2>

				<br />

				<h3>Search for Books:</h3>
				<ul style="margin-left: 20px;">
					<li><b>1.Choose the library:</b> The library name that your
						books would be.
						<li><b>2.Choose search category:</b> This could be books'
							title, author or barcode.</li>
						<li><b>3.Enter the keyword:</b> Not case sensitive</li>
				</ul>

				<br />

				<h3>Get Shortest Path:</h3>
				<p>Just add the book to operation list. Then the path will be
					displayed on the map area.</p>

