				<br />
				<h2>Add book</h2>
				<p>Only the Curator and Senior Librarian can add a book to
					database. To add a book, please go to the 'Books' page.</p>

				<br />

				<h2>Edit Map</h2>
				<p>Only the Curator and database administer can edit maps. To
					edit maps, please go to the 'Maps' page.</p>

				<ul style="margin-left: 20px;">
					<li><b>Add stuff to the map:</b> Drag the stuff to the map.</li>
					<li><b>Draw map:</b> In the main body of map page, hold the
						left button of mouse and move.</li>
					<li><b>Add text:</b> Double click the map, you can add a text.</li>
				</ul>
